overview: Gaspard Berthille is the director of Tout-Paris, a famous cabaret that maintains the myth of wild Parisian nights. But unlike his father, Dary, Gaspard has not been able to perpetuate the reputation of the establishment. The arrival of a new investor, accompanied by his son, will shake up Gaspard and profoundly change the lives and destinies of the entire Tout-Paris team.
